242
00:17:15,959 --> 00:17:16,839
Nona-Nona.

243
00:17:17,310 --> 00:17:19,350
Keluarga Xie datang
mengunjungi Nona.

244
00:17:20,280 --> 00:17:20,839
Gawat.

