00:19:37,959 --> 00:19:40,760
Setelah menikah, kau hanya
perlu mengurus rumah.

301
00:19:40,959 --> 00:19:42,520
Apanya membedakan benar dan salah?

302
00:19:42,520 --> 00:19:43,330
Aku tak mau menikah.

303
00:19:43,400 --> 00:19:44,199
Kau harus menikah.

304
00:19:44,199 --> 00:19:46,400
Pokoknya aku tak mau menikah.
Kalau kau memaksaku lagi…

305
00:19:46,400 --> 00:19:46,920
Jangan.

306
00:19:47,160 --> 00:19:48,800
Kau paksa lagi,
aku akan lompat ke sungai.

307
00:19:48,800 --> 00:19:49,239
Kau…

308
00:19:49,239 --> 00:19:49,760
Xiaoman.

309
