00:19:53,839 --> 00:19:54,239
Cepatlah.

314
00:19:54,239 --> 00:19:54,599
Xiaoman.

315
00:19:54,599 --> 00:19:55,280
Ikuti dia.

316
00:19:56,050 --> 00:19:57,400
Lihatlah anak yang kau besarkan.

317
00:19:58,500 --> 00:19:59,890
Memangnya dia bukan anakmu?

318
