356
00:21:54,520 --> 00:21:55,650
Ulang tahun ayah Yan Boyang.

357
00:21:57,150 --> 00:21:58,250
Kita mau ucapkan selamat.

358
00:21:59,040 --> 00:21:59,560
Benarkah?

